codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand latin grammar. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. accipere, ac~isse, ac~um esse Choose from this set of possible answers [ cēp cept, aus, abstul ablāt, bib, statu statūt, tetig tāct] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'cēp cept', 'aus', 'abstul ablāt', 'bib', 'statu statūt', 'tetig tāct']
